				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$r_0=0.996R_{\odot }$$\end{document} and have peaks strengths of 380±30G\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
