Despite the ambiguity caused by the surface term, detailed modelling gives more precise estimates of the properties of a star. Of course grid modelling is also affected by the surface term, but to a lesser degree since the term gets reduced in the process of calculating the average value of Δν\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
